    <div>
      <h3>Equipping letter carriers with the right tools</h3>
      <p>
        To assist with effective check-ins, postal workers will be provided with
        an app that includes details about the people they are visiting, a form
        to report check-ins, and emergency contacts as well as resources to
        better equip them for unexpected situations. The check-in report is made
        to be as short-handed as possible to ensure that postal workers may fill
        them out while they are on the go.
      </p>
